cancel

void cancel(int versionNo)
            throws InformationalException
Logically deletes the object, i.e. transitions its record status from RECORDSTATUSEntry.NORMAL to RECORDSTATUSEntry.CANCELLED.

Parameters:
versionNo - The version number of the object being cancelled.
Throws:
InformationalException - if any application validation errors are found during the cancel operation, e.g. if the object is already cancelled.
